  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390420/extras/da844faad25a710a4edec1af14548cf4.poster.avif?t=1772926529\" width=630 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390420/extras/da844faad25a710a4edec1af14548cf4.webm?t=1772926529\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390420/extras/da844faad25a710a4edec1af14548cf4.mp4?t=1772926529\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BILLY SAVES THE WORLD gives you ULTIMATE FREEDOM</strong>   </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>>>Take a slower approach and explore a hand crafted open-ish world.</strong><br><strong>>>Solve puzzles and help dozens of unique NPCs through rich (hilarious & heartfelt) side-quests</strong><br><strong>>>Beat challenging old-school platforming stages (plus time trials!)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All of the above will earn you \"SP\" that you can use to purchase upgrades and new abilities to help you progress. This means you can prioritize puzzles over platforming, or, if you hate puzzles, skip them in favor of action. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>How you play is entirely up to you.</strong> <br>       <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390420/extras/a606684a4290819124a5bfa3024a67f0.poster.avif?t=1772926529\" width=630 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390420/extras/a606684a4290819124a5bfa3024a67f0.webm?t=1772926529\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390420/extras/a606684a4290819124a5bfa3024a67f0.mp4?t=1772926529\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A NARRATIVE-DRIVEN platformer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The story itself may seem silly, simple, and superficial on the surface but those who roll credits will be taken on a surprisingly emotional ride, one that you won't regret taking. <br><br>Oh, and you'll save the world, too.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390420/extras/9c97ff5efcb957651b9e837312c11d8b.avif?t=1772926529\" width=630 height=122 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>FEATURING ONE OF THE YEAR'S BEST SOUNDTRACKS.</u></strong> Composed by John McMillan (Assassin's Creed IV: Black Flag) and multi-platinum producer, Tom Ratesic (Nicki Minaj, Lil Wayne).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>INSPIRED BY \"FUTURAMA\" AND \"CURSE OF MONKEY ISLAND\"</u></strong><u>.</u> Choose your dialogue in this comedic sci-fi love story written by <strong>award-winning filmmaker, Cooper Bibaud. </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>TOP FILM & TV ANIMATORS.</u> </strong>Run, Slide, Jump, Rocket-Boost, Wall-Jump, and use Jedi-like super powers to explore a dense 2D open-ish world, featuring 7+ diverse biomes with beautifully hand drawn environments and frame by frame animation.<strong></strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390420/extras/d755022d836124dd437c772c7e4753f6.poster.avif?t=1772926529\" width=630 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390420/extras/d755022d836124dd437c772c7e4753f6.webm?t=1772926529\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390420/extras/d755022d836124dd437c772c7e4753f6.mp4?t=1772926529\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve over <strong>25 side-quests</strong> with multiple dialogue branches, solutions and outcomes based on what you say and do. Packed with <strong>30+ optional levels to beat</strong>, each containing different routes<strong>,</strong> unique enemies, deadly traps, creative puzzles, secret collectibles, and nail biting time trials. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An average of <strong>8 hours</strong> <strong>of gameplay</strong> (and well over 20+ for completionists). <i>Wowee!</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390420/extras/02533f6f19b9d8bde4e8c03e6b929492.avif?t=1772926529\" width=630 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Join the official Discord channel for the latest news & announcements, chat directly with the creator, PLUS receive exclusive videos, images, WIPs and more.</strong></u> <br>  </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390420/extras/da844faad25a710a4edec1af14548cf4.poster.avif?t=1772926529\" width=630 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390420/extras/da844faad25a710a4edec1af14548cf4.webm?t=1772926529\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390420/extras/da844faad25a710a4edec1af14548cf4.mp4?t=1772926529\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BILLY SAVES THE WORLD gives you ULTIMATE FREEDOM</strong>   </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>>>Take a slower approach and explore a hand crafted open-ish world.</strong><br><strong>>>Solve puzzles and help dozens of unique NPCs through rich (hilarious & heartfelt) side-quests</strong><br><strong>>>Beat challenging old-school platforming stages (plus time trials!)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All of the above will earn you \"SP\" that you can use to purchase upgrades and new abilities to help you progress. This means you can prioritize puzzles over platforming, or, if you hate puzzles, skip them in favor of action. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>How you play is entirely up to you.</strong> <br>       <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390420/extras/a606684a4290819124a5bfa3024a67f0.poster.avif?t=1772926529\" width=630 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390420/extras/a606684a4290819124a5bfa3024a67f0.webm?t=1772926529\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390420/extras/a606684a4290819124a5bfa3024a