i.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390420/extras/d755022d836124dd437c772c7e4753f6.mp4?t=1772926529\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve over <strong>25 side-quests</strong> with multiple dialogue branches, solutions and outcomes based on what you say and do. Packed with <strong>30+ optional levels to beat</strong>, each containing different routes<strong>,</strong> unique enemies, deadly traps, creative puzzles, secret collectibles, and nail biting time trials. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An average of <strong>8 hours</strong> <strong>of gameplay</strong> (and well over 20+ for completionists). <i>Wowee!</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390420/extras/02533f6f19b9d8bde4e8c03e6b929492.avif?t=1772926529\" width=630 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Join the official Discord channel for the latest news & announcements, chat directly with the creator, PLUS receive exclusive videos, images, WIPs and more.</strong></u> <br>  </p>",
